<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Takopi no Genzai</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://jkp.my.id/assets//img//icons/favico.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Varela+Round&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>
    <style>
        h1,
        h2 {
            font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
    <section
        class="relative w-full h-screen flex flex-col  md:px-16 pb-4 bg-cover bg-center"
        style="background-image: url('../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/bg.webp');">

        <!-- Overlay Gradient -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-pink-800 via-black/50 to-transparent"></div>

        <!-- TOP (70%) -->
        <div class="relative h-2/3  flex items-end md:p-4 z-10">
            <div class=" px-4 flex flex-col text-white">
                <!-- Judul Jepang (besar) -->
                <h1 class="md:text-5xl text-4xl font-bold p-2 text-pink-500 text-shadow-md text-shadow-white drop-shadow-md drop-shadow-black/75">
                    タコピーの原罪
                </h1>
                <!-- Judul Latin (kecil) -->
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold p-2 pt-0">
                    Takopii no Genzai
                </h2>
                <!-- Info -->
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-200/85 px-2 font-bold">
                    2025 | 17+ | 12 Ep | 24 m / Ep | JP
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BOTTOM (30%) -->
        <div class="relative h-1/3 w-full md:flex-row flex-col px-4 max-sm:px-0 flex gap-4 z-10 text-white">

            <!-- Ilustrasi (Desktop only) -->
            <div class=" px-4 flex items-center justify-center h-full max-lg:hidden">
                <div class=" h-full aspect-[2/3]">
                    <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/cover.webp"
                        alt="Cover"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Deskripsi -->
            <div class="flex-1  flex flex-col p-4 max-w-3xl">
                <!-- Penulis -->
                <div class="font-bold p-2">
                    Dir. Shinya Iino
                </div>
                <!-- Sinopsis -->
                <div class="flex-1  p-2">
                    Takopi no Genzai (Takopi’s Original Sin) adalah sebuah manga dan anime pendek yang mengangkat tema gelap tentang penderitaan, kesepian, dan pencarian makna hidup. Cerita dimulai dengan kedatangan Takopi, seorang alien dari Planet Happy, yang bertujuan untuk menyebarkan kebahagiaan di Bumi. Ia bertemu dengan Shizuka Kuze, seorang gadis 9 tahun yang dibuli di sekolah dan hanya memiliki anjing peliharaan bernama Chappy sebagai teman sejatinya.
                </div>
                <!-- Genre Buttons -->
                <div class="flex gap-2 p-2 flex-wrap">
                    <span class="px-3 font-bold py-1 rounded-full border-2 border-white text-white cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:text-pink-400 transition">
                        Drama
                    </span>
                    <span class="px-3 font-bold py-1 rounded-full border-2 border-white text-white cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:text-pink-400 transition">
                        Psychological
                    </span>
                    <span class="px-3 font-bold py-1 rounded-full border-2 border-white text-white cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:text-pink-400 transition">
                        Sci-Fi
                    </span>
                    <span class="px-3 font-bold py-1 rounded-full border-2 border-white text-white cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:text-pink-400 transition">
                        Time Travel
                    </span>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- Score (Desktop only) -->
            <div class="lg:flex hidden flex-col items-center justify-center ml-auto">
                <!-- Lingkaran + score di tengah -->
                <a href="https://myanimelist.net/anime/60489/Takopii_no_Genzai" aria-label="Lihat di MyAnimeList" target="_blank">
                    <div class="relative w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <!-- Background Circle -->
                        <svg class="absolute w-full h-full -rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
                            <circle
                                class="text-gray-300"
                                stroke-width="4"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                fill="none"
                                cx="18"
                                cy="18"
                                r="16" />
                        </svg>

                        <!-- Foreground Circle -->
                        <svg class="absolute w-full h-full -rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
                            <circle
                                class="text-yellow-400"
                                stroke-width="4"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                fill="none"
                                cx="18"
                                cy="18"
                                r="16"
                                stroke-dasharray="100"
                                stroke-dashoffset="11"
                                stroke-linecap="round" />
                        </svg>

                        <!-- Score Text di tengah lingkaran -->
                        <div class="relative text-lg font-bold text-white">
                            8.91
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Text di bawah lingkaran -->
                <div class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">
                    MAL
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

    <!-- Poster & Score untuk Mobile -->
    <div class="lg:hidden bg-pink-800 flex justify-around items-center p-6 max-sm:pt-52 gap-4">
        <!-- Poster -->
        <div class=" aspect-[2/3] w-40">
            <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/cover.webp"
                alt="Cover"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <!-- Score -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <!-- Lingkaran + score di tengah -->
            <a href="https://myanimelist.net/anime/60489/Takopii_no_Genzai" aria-label="Lihat di MyAnimeList" target="_blank">
                <div class="relative w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <!-- Background Circle -->
                    <svg class="absolute w-full h-full -rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
                        <circle
                            class="text-gray-300"
                            stroke-width="4"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            fill="none"
                            cx="18"
                            cy="18"
                            r="16" />
                    </svg>

                    <!-- Foreground Circle -->
                    <svg class="absolute w-full h-full -rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
                        <circle
                            class="text-yellow-400"
                            stroke-width="4"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            fill="none"
                            cx="18"
                            cy="18"
                            r="16"
                            stroke-dasharray="100"
                            stroke-dashoffset="11"
                            stroke-linecap="round" />
                    </svg>

                    <!-- Score Text di tengah lingkaran -->
                    <div class="relative text-lg font-bold text-white">
                        8.91
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Text di bawah lingkaran -->
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">
                MAL
            </div>
        </div>



    </div>


    <section class="w-full  bg-pink-800  p-6 pb-0">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 md gap-2 ">

            <!-- Loop 8 gambar pertama (selalu tampil) -->
            <div class=" aspect-video">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/02.webp" alt="Shizuka tertidur"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-video">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/04.webp" alt="Shizuka di kelas"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-video">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/03.webp" alt="Shizuka dan Chappy"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-video">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/11.webp" alt="Marina di rumah"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-video">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/09.webp" alt="Alat ajaib Takopi"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-video">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/06.webp" alt="Shizuka"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>

            <!-- Gambar ke-7-8 (hidden di mobile) -->
            <div class=" aspect-video hidden md:block">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/07.webp" alt="Shizuka dan Takopi
                    class=" w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-video hidden md:block">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/05.webp" alt="Naoki"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>

            <!-- Gambar ke-9 (hidden di tablet) -->
            <div class=" aspect-video hidden lg:block">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/10.webp" alt="Marina"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>


    <section class=" py-8 bg-pink-800">
        <div class=" max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center px-6">
            <p class=" text-lg leading-relaxed text-white">
                Anime ini berhasil menyampaikan pesan universal mengenai empati, pentingnya komunikasi, dan kekuatan tindakan kecil yang tulus dalam memperbaiki kehidupan orang lain.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="w-full pt-4 flex flex-col gap-4 bg-gray-100">

        <!-- Bagian Atas -->
        <div class=" flex justify-between max-md:flex-col gap-2 items-center py-4 px-8">
            <!-- Judul -->
            <h2 class=" text-xl text-pink-900">
                タコピーの原罪 <span class="font-bold">| Takopii no Genzai</span>
            </h2>
            <!-- Icon Media Sosial -->
            <div class=" flex gap-4">
                <a href="https://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/takopi_project/" aria-label="Kunjugi Website Resmi" target="_blank" class="border- w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="domain">
                </a>
                <a href="https://x.com/takopi_pr" aria-label="Kunjungi Twitter Resmi" target="_blank" class="border- w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" x="0px" y="0px" width="50" height="50" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
                        <path d="M 6.9199219 6 L 21.136719 26.726562 L 6.2285156 44 L 9.40625 44 L 22.544922 28.777344 L 32.986328 44 L 43 44 L 28.123047 22.3125 L 42.203125 6 L 39.027344 6 L 26.716797 20.261719 L 16.933594 6 L 6.9199219 6 z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bagian Bawah (Kotak Gambar) -->
        <div class="  grid grid-cols-4 max-lg:grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-4">
            <div class=" aspect-square">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/13.webp"
                    alt="Shizuka kehilangan Chappy"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover border-" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-square hidden md:block">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/08.webp"
                    alt="Shizuka, Takopi, dan Chappy"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover border-" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-square hidden lg:block">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/12.webp"
                    alt="RPI Marina"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover border-" />
            </div>
            <div class=" aspect-square hidden lg:block">
                <img src="../assets/img/Takopi-no-Genzai/01.webp"
                    alt="Pertemuan Shizuka dengan Takopi"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover border-" />
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 text-center text-xs md:mt-4 py-5">
        <p>
            © <span id="year"></span> JKP Project —
            Icon by <a href="https://icons8.com" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">Icons8</a> —
            Design by <a href="https://x.com/DearRev_" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">@DearRev_</a>
        </p>

        <script>
            document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
        </script>
    </footer>



</body>

</html>